Here‚Äôs little old me doing a Q&A for them, talking about my artistic process, favourite pieces in the collection and how I‚Äôll be wearing them this season üå∏

Have you listened to my new single? ‚ÄòYour Bed‚Äô is available to stream and listen on all platforms! Link in bio. 
Always so exciting bringing out new music, and seeing the long labour of love that goes into every part of it. Please share and enjoy! 
Thankyou @stbadstbad for production & co-writing, and @lydiaxcollins for the photography. And thanks for all the arguments @jamiekaii hahaha that spurred this song on üòÇüå∏‚ú®üéà‚ö°Ô∏èüåû

node.text:
A snippet of a recent song I‚Äôve been writing, inspired by the lovely @grace___hazel‚Äôs awakening course. I‚Äôve been working on learning to truly love my body, knowing what honour and respect it deserves; a healing of the past and celebration of the present! 
I came to terms with quite a lot of past sexual upset & memories that hurt, and all I want for my little girl is to teach her how to be open, loving, and know what she deserves in a partner! Beautiful to have such an opportunity to learn and pass a message on. 
Sending my love to all of our younger selves who maybe had to learn the hard way, and to all of those who still at present feel disconnect, confusion, pain, numbness or judgement in terms of their body or femininity (or masculinity). Always keep exploring and expanding üß°

node.text: Happy belated Fathers Day to the best man I know. It‚Äôs an honour and a pleasure to walk side by side in this life with you, and have created two beautiful children.
